WEBVTT

01:35.440 --> 01:36.700
Attention, everyone!

01:37.080 --> 01:38.000
Attention!

02:02.080 --> 02:03.280
Reporting to the brigade commander,

02:03.280 --> 02:05.240
the regimental direct unit has assembled.

02:05.240 --> 02:07.040
Please give your instructions.

02:46.960 --> 02:48.120
I am Zhang Yunkui.

02:48.880 --> 02:50.280
I make a pact with you all.

02:50.600 --> 02:51.930
In the face of the enemy,

02:52.160 --> 02:53.480
whatever happened in the past,

02:53.480 --> 02:54.960
let bygones be bygones.

02:55.480 --> 02:56.680
But from today on,

02:56.840 --> 02:59.040
I will go to the battlefield with you all

02:59.079 --> 03:00.280
to repay our country.

03:00.280 --> 03:01.520
We live and die together.

03:01.520 --> 03:02.560
Never retreat.

03:05.680 --> 03:06.680
Do you agree?

03:07.000 --> 03:07.800
Yes!

03:08.160 --> 03:08.890
Do you agree?

03:09.000 --> 03:09.960
Yes!

03:11.240 --> 03:12.040
Commander Liu.

03:12.040 --> 03:12.640
Here.

03:13.120 --> 03:14.680
How should deserters be dealt with?

03:14.680 --> 03:16.360
During wartime, to enforce military discipline,

03:16.360 --> 03:17.320
captured deserters

03:17.320 --> 03:18.850
can be executed on the spot.

03:31.560 --> 03:33.090
Do you have anything to say?

03:36.800 --> 03:38.800
The leading officer, step forward.

03:39.360 --> 03:40.079
Here.

03:40.160 --> 03:40.960
Execute them.

03:41.480 --> 03:42.079
Yes, sir.

03:43.840 --> 03:45.320
I'm innocent!

03:45.360 --> 03:46.440
I'm not a soldier!

03:46.640 --> 03:48.440
I was forced to come here!

03:49.240 --> 03:50.240
I'm not a soldier!

03:50.240 --> 03:50.560
Wait.

03:50.560 --> 03:50.960
Shut up!

03:50.960 --> 03:51.680
I was forced!

03:51.680 --> 03:52.640
Stop him.

04:02.600 --> 04:04.330
What's going on? Make it clear.

04:04.560 --> 04:08.280
I'm just a cook at Zhengxing Restaurant.

04:09.440 --> 04:11.400
I was walking on the street,

04:11.520 --> 04:14.800
and they grabbed me.

04:15.720 --> 04:16.680
Who grabbed you?

04:17.200 --> 04:18.240
I dare not say.

04:19.279 --> 04:20.040
Adjutant Zhao.

04:20.040 --> 04:20.720
Here.

04:24.680 --> 04:25.440
Don't move.

04:25.920 --> 04:26.880
Don't move.

04:34.800 --> 04:35.800
Speak.

04:35.880 --> 04:36.920
Who grabbed you?

04:40.760 --> 04:41.600
Speak.

04:45.560 --> 04:46.480
It's him.

04:47.080 --> 04:47.920
It's him.

04:48.120 --> 04:49.880
He forced me to lie

04:50.080 --> 04:51.600
and say I volunteered.

04:52.280 --> 04:53.159
If I spilled the beans,

04:53.159 --> 04:54.680
he said he'd kill me.

04:54.680 --> 04:55.720
It's him.

04:55.720 --> 04:56.840
Who else?

04:58.040 --> 04:58.800
And...

04:59.280 --> 05:00.200
And...

05:00.720 --> 05:01.560
And...

05:01.880 --> 05:02.720
And...

05:03.040 --> 05:04.560
And...

05:08.520 --> 05:09.520
Come here.

05:10.400 --> 05:11.160
Him.

05:11.640 --> 05:13.600
He hit me with the butt of his gun.

05:13.920 --> 05:14.760
And...

05:15.160 --> 05:16.320
And...

05:16.360 --> 05:17.320
And...

05:21.760 --> 05:22.560
Him.

05:22.840 --> 05:23.680
He kicked me.

05:24.000 --> 05:25.040
He kicked me.

05:25.800 --> 05:26.400
Let go.

05:26.440 --> 05:27.240
And...

05:27.720 --> 05:28.400
And...

05:29.120 --> 05:29.880
And...

05:31.520 --> 05:32.640
And him.

05:32.720 --> 05:34.080
Come out.

05:34.760 --> 05:35.880
He's just like him.

05:36.320 --> 05:37.920
Said he'd kill me.

05:38.440 --> 05:39.280
Officer!

05:39.600 --> 05:40.960
Your Honor!

05:41.400 --> 05:43.520
Please help me!

05:43.920 --> 05:45.640
Help me!

05:46.120 --> 05:46.980
Commander Liu.

05:47.080 --> 05:47.800
Here.

05:48.320 --> 05:49.560
How many men like this

05:49.560 --> 05:51.560
have you forcibly drafted in total?

05:56.680 --> 05:58.120
Taking phantom payrolls,

05:58.120 --> 05:58.920
afraid of being investigated,

05:58.920 --> 06:01.120
so you kidnap men to make up the numbers.

06:01.400 --> 06:02.480
What time is it now?

06:02.480 --> 06:04.340
Tell me the truth, Commander Liu.

06:09.800 --> 06:11.360
Reporting to the Brigadier.

06:11.360 --> 06:13.800
We haven't been able to replenish our recruits.

06:13.800 --> 06:15.200
This was our only option.

06:15.520 --> 06:17.320
There are probably about

06:17.320 --> 06:19.120
two hundred of them in the whole regiment.

06:19.120 --> 06:22.040
Their names have already been registered and reported.

06:22.040 --> 06:23.320
You really have the nerve.

06:23.320 --> 06:24.200
Yes.

06:25.680 --> 06:27.340
We're already understaffed,

06:27.880 --> 06:29.610
and facing a formidable enemy.

06:29.920 --> 06:31.200
If we let them go now,

06:31.760 --> 06:34.040
we really won't be able to fight this battle.

06:34.040 --> 06:35.200
Actually,

06:35.200 --> 06:36.120
the higher-ups

06:36.680 --> 06:37.800
also turn a blind eye

06:37.800 --> 06:38.920
to this.

06:45.760 --> 06:46.920
Try your best to persuade them.

06:46.920 --> 06:48.120
Keep those who are willing to stay.

06:48.120 --> 06:49.240
For those who really don't want to,

06:49.240 --> 06:51.000
don't assign them to combat units.

06:51.000 --> 06:52.600
Compile a list and give it to me.

06:52.600 --> 06:53.600
I will report it

06:53.880 --> 06:55.480
and try to get them all released.

06:55.480 --> 06:56.240
Yes.

06:57.240 --> 06:58.440
Your Honor!

06:58.640 --> 07:00.720
I beg you, please let me go!

07:01.200 --> 07:01.920
I...

07:02.440 --> 07:04.120
Your Honor, look,

07:04.240 --> 07:06.280
I was supposed to get married.

07:06.640 --> 07:08.560
I made a brand new gown,

07:08.720 --> 07:10.720
just for the wedding.

07:10.720 --> 07:12.840
But then they grabbed me.

07:13.160 --> 07:15.400
Your Honor, I beg you, let me go!

07:15.440 --> 07:16.160
Let me go!

07:16.320 --> 07:17.880
Let me go!

07:19.840 --> 07:21.240
I just promised

07:21.280 --> 07:22.740
to let bygones be bygones.

07:23.160 --> 07:24.200
I can overlook

07:24.720 --> 07:26.200
the fact that you kidnapped men.

07:26.200 --> 07:27.400
But there is one thing

07:27.720 --> 07:29.520
I must hold you accountable for.

07:30.160 --> 07:31.000
You killed him

07:31.120 --> 07:33.280
because he was a deserter and deserved to die.

07:33.280 --> 07:34.320
But Company Commander Yu.

07:34.320 --> 07:35.000
Here.

07:35.120 --> 07:36.360
I just said wait.

07:36.840 --> 07:38.159
Why did you still insist on firing?

07:38.159 --> 07:39.560
What did you mean by that?

07:46.080 --> 07:47.140
What are you doing?

07:47.240 --> 07:48.120
What?

07:49.240 --> 07:49.960
Arrest him.

07:50.000 --> 07:50.680
Move.

07:50.800 --> 07:51.400
Let go!

07:51.520 --> 07:52.600
Company Commander Yu.

07:52.600 --> 07:54.200
Not only did you violate military regulations,

07:54.200 --> 07:55.760
but you also tried to silence him.

07:55.760 --> 07:57.159
You belittle the lives of others,

07:57.159 --> 07:58.760
insulting the identity of a soldier.

07:58.760 --> 07:59.920
According to military law,

07:59.920 --> 08:01.520
how should you be dealt with?

08:01.840 --> 08:03.120
Is his life not a life?

08:03.640 --> 08:05.900
It's not worth trading your life for his.

08:08.240 --> 08:09.160
What do you mean?

08:09.160 --> 08:10.560
Are you going to shoot me?

08:11.360 --> 08:13.040
Yu Yuansheng, shut up.

08:15.600 --> 08:16.400
Brigadier.

08:21.800 --> 08:24.800
The Brigadier is using me to establish his authority.

08:30.680 --> 08:31.480
Fine.

08:32.120 --> 08:32.980
In this matter,

08:33.799 --> 08:35.480
I, Old Yu, was out of line.

08:36.080 --> 08:37.210
If the new commander

08:37.720 --> 08:39.580
can lead the brothers to victory,

08:39.840 --> 08:40.679
I, Old Yu,

08:41.400 --> 08:44.530
will serve as a sacrifice to the flag of the 87th Brigade.

08:44.720 --> 08:45.920
I have nothing to say.

08:50.440 --> 08:51.120
Let's go.

08:51.520 --> 08:52.280
Move.

08:52.360 --> 08:53.960
Bring a message to my mother.

08:54.360 --> 08:55.400
Tell her,

08:55.680 --> 08:56.360
Kneel.

08:56.440 --> 08:57.880
that I died in battle.

09:03.480 --> 09:04.280
Wait.

09:07.320 --> 09:07.980
Brigadier,

09:08.040 --> 09:09.960
this kid Yu is a good fighter.

09:10.560 --> 09:11.480
With a formidable enemy ahead,

09:11.480 --> 09:12.480
if we kill him now,

09:12.600 --> 09:13.930
it would be a great pity.

09:15.600 --> 09:16.520
Brigadier.

09:22.840 --> 09:23.760
Yu Yuansheng,

09:24.360 --> 09:26.160
do you have anything else to say?

09:26.360 --> 09:27.490
Report, Brigadier.

09:29.200 --> 09:31.000
I want to die on the battlefield.

09:35.160 --> 09:36.160
Soldiers,

09:37.720 --> 09:38.960
the Japanese have already reached

09:38.960 --> 09:39.920
our doorstep.

09:40.440 --> 09:42.400
I don't care how you got here today,

09:42.720 --> 09:43.980
I, Yunkui, implore you

09:44.400 --> 09:45.960
to fight the enemy with me.

09:46.720 --> 09:47.680
According to military regulations,

09:47.680 --> 09:49.640
Yu Yuansheng should be executed on the spot.

09:49.640 --> 09:51.370
But a great battle is imminent.

09:51.600 --> 09:53.240
Do you think he deserves to die?

09:53.240 --> 09:54.040
Yes.

09:55.080 --> 09:55.960
Does he?

09:56.000 --> 09:57.040
He does.

09:57.560 --> 09:58.690
Where should he die?

09:58.760 --> 09:59.960
On the battlefield!

10:00.120 --> 10:00.920
Where?

10:01.000 --> 10:02.040
The battlefield!

10:05.440 --> 10:06.240
Yu Yuansheng!

10:06.280 --> 10:07.000
Here!

10:07.280 --> 10:08.140
Let me tell you,

10:08.640 --> 10:10.370
I didn't spare your life today.

10:10.840 --> 10:12.520
It's because your brothers pleaded for you

10:12.520 --> 10:13.520
that I spared you.

10:13.960 --> 10:14.820
Remember that.

10:15.040 --> 10:15.920
I will.

10:16.440 --> 10:17.570
Return to your unit.

10:28.560 --> 10:30.080
The impact points are scattered.

10:30.080 --> 10:31.520
Large-caliber naval guns.

10:31.520 --> 10:32.880
This proves that the Japanese

10:32.880 --> 10:34.000
are about to land.

10:34.440 --> 10:36.640
Luodian must be in a state of emergency.

10:36.880 --> 10:37.520
Soon,

10:37.720 --> 10:39.640
you will receive orders to move out.

10:39.640 --> 10:40.320
Everyone,

10:40.320 --> 10:41.120
prepare for battle.

10:41.120 --> 10:42.240
Report!

10:44.840 --> 10:45.840
Report, Brigadier.

10:45.840 --> 10:46.920
An urgent telegram from division headquarters.

10:46.920 --> 10:49.120
The Japanese have landed in the direction of Wusong.

10:49.120 --> 10:50.480
Our brigade is ordered to move out immediately

10:50.480 --> 10:51.740
to reinforce Luodian.

10:53.880 --> 10:54.920
Company Commander of the Infantry Artillery!

10:54.920 --> 10:55.680
Here!

10:56.800 --> 10:57.640
How much ammunition is left?

10:57.640 --> 10:58.640
Since the troops just arrived,

10:58.640 --> 11:00.520
rear supplies are not fully in place yet.

11:00.520 --> 11:01.320
Currently,

11:01.440 --> 11:02.960
I only have two units of shells.

11:02.960 --> 11:04.040
Take all the ammunition

11:04.040 --> 11:05.240
and follow the vanguard battalion.

11:05.240 --> 11:05.920
Yes, sir.

11:06.320 --> 11:07.360
Commander Liu, Commander Feng.

11:07.360 --> 11:07.960
Here.

11:08.120 --> 11:08.760
Here.

11:08.800 --> 11:10.160
Notify everyone in the unit,

11:10.160 --> 11:11.280
check weapons and equipment,

11:11.280 --> 11:12.080
and supplies.

11:12.200 --> 11:13.120
In half an hour,

11:13.400 --> 11:14.160
we assemble and head out.

11:14.160 --> 11:14.690
Yes, sir.

11:18.160 --> 11:19.320
My righteous lord,

11:19.680 --> 11:20.800
my righteous lord,

11:21.600 --> 11:22.480
my lord!

11:23.320 --> 11:24.380
My righteous lord,

11:24.440 --> 11:25.520
my righteous lord,

11:25.920 --> 11:26.980
my righteous lord!

11:28.760 --> 11:29.760
Eyes front!

11:30.880 --> 11:31.240
Quick

11:31.240 --> 11:32.200
march!

11:32.200 --> 11:33.800
Run again, and I'll kill you.

11:33.800 --> 11:35.000
Is there any law left?

11:35.440 --> 11:36.800
The lord said I could go!

11:37.240 --> 11:38.000
My lord!

11:38.160 --> 11:39.760
Someone is using public office for personal revenge!

11:39.760 --> 11:41.120
What are you crying for?

11:41.240 --> 11:42.700
Can you cry louder than me?

11:43.040 --> 11:44.240
You are assigned to the logistics team.

11:44.240 --> 11:45.680
Return to your unit and move out immediately.

11:45.680 --> 11:47.280
Why waste your breath on him?

11:49.800 --> 11:51.160
Officer, he knows he's wrong.

11:51.160 --> 11:51.840
Move out.

11:51.880 --> 11:52.840
Keep up.

11:52.880 --> 11:53.940
Keep up, everyone.

11:54.440 --> 11:55.120
Hurry up.

11:56.280 --> 11:57.120
Hurry up.

11:58.360 --> 11:59.090
Here will do.

11:59.640 --> 12:00.960
Quick, here.

12:01.960 --> 12:02.560
Keep up.

12:03.600 --> 12:04.280
Careful.

12:04.440 --> 12:04.880
Careful.

12:04.880 --> 12:05.560
Make way.

12:06.840 --> 12:07.440
Quick.

12:07.680 --> 12:08.680
Careful.

12:08.880 --> 12:09.560
You can't go in.

12:09.560 --> 12:11.080
This is a field hospital, no casual entry.

12:11.080 --> 12:11.880
Go back.

12:11.960 --> 12:13.960
We have a letter of recommendation.

12:15.200 --> 12:16.080
Are you together?

12:16.080 --> 12:16.640
Yes.

12:16.640 --> 12:17.440
We are together.

12:17.440 --> 12:18.240
Wait a moment.

12:18.400 --> 12:19.120
Dr. Sun.

12:19.120 --> 12:20.760
Dr. Sun.

12:22.200 --> 12:24.930
Some people brought a letter of recommendation.

12:27.480 --> 12:28.360
Sun Zheng.

12:28.680 --> 12:29.240
Luo Zuliang.

12:29.240 --> 12:30.040
Wang Jianguang.

12:30.040 --> 12:30.960
It's all written on there.

12:30.960 --> 12:31.800
It's written on there.

12:31.800 --> 12:32.760
Wang Jianguang.

12:33.240 --> 12:34.400
Okay, follow me.

12:36.000 --> 12:37.080
Let us in too.

12:39.320 --> 12:40.320
Go back.

12:40.360 --> 12:41.640
Let us in, officer.

12:41.640 --> 12:42.720
What year are you in?

12:42.720 --> 12:43.440
I am a third-year student.

12:43.440 --> 12:45.000
They are second-year students.

12:45.000 --> 12:45.720
What can you do?

12:45.720 --> 12:46.840
We've done simple surgeries,

12:46.840 --> 12:49.100
but our clinical experience is lacking.

12:49.320 --> 12:50.920
Help take care of the wounded first,

12:50.920 --> 12:52.360
then take turns observing surgeries.

12:52.360 --> 12:52.960
Okay.

12:53.320 --> 12:54.040
Dr. Sun,

12:54.200 --> 12:56.440
a wounded soldier over there is not doing well.

12:56.440 --> 12:57.320
Go through this courtyard

12:57.320 --> 12:58.880
and find Director Wang in the operating room in the back.

12:58.880 --> 12:59.760
Okay.

13:01.760 --> 13:02.400
Excuse me.

13:02.440 --> 13:03.360
Excuse me.

13:03.480 --> 13:04.920
We medical students can be of great use.

13:04.920 --> 13:05.640
My shoe came off.

13:05.640 --> 13:07.200
Sun, you're a history major.

13:07.200 --> 13:08.640
Aren't you just making a mess here?

13:08.640 --> 13:09.480
I can be like them,

13:09.480 --> 13:10.680
and help move things.

15:02.520 --> 15:03.360
Brothers!

16:16.280 --> 16:18.120
Yunkui, well done.

16:18.560 --> 16:20.160
In the first battle of your new post,

16:20.160 --> 16:22.220
you seized the Bai family residence.

16:22.280 --> 16:25.440
This greatly relieved the pressure on the neighboring troops.

16:25.440 --> 16:27.960
You've made a great start as the new brigade commander.

16:27.960 --> 16:30.020
I will apply to the army headquarters

16:30.440 --> 16:31.900
to request a merit for you.

16:32.240 --> 16:33.900
But you must hold your ground.

16:34.120 --> 16:36.520
The Bai family residence is the junction

16:36.520 --> 16:37.680
with the right-wing troops.

16:37.680 --> 16:41.240
The Japanese army will definitely choose to break through here.

16:41.240 --> 16:42.760
You must not yield

16:42.920 --> 16:44.120
an inch of ground.

16:44.120 --> 16:44.960
Commander.

16:45.120 --> 16:46.240
The troops have suffered heavy losses.

16:46.240 --> 16:47.360
Without heavy firepower support,

16:47.360 --> 16:49.600
please assign the division's artillery to me.

16:49.600 --> 16:53.000
Yunkui, the division's artillery has run out of ammunition.

16:53.200 --> 16:54.440
They are out of supplies.

16:54.440 --> 16:55.520
Now everything

16:55.960 --> 16:57.560
depends on yourselves.

16:57.840 --> 16:58.640
Commander.

16:59.040 --> 17:01.120
If there are no cannons, give me a battalion.

17:01.120 --> 17:02.280
Send me some more men,

17:02.280 --> 17:03.080
especially veterans.

17:03.080 --> 17:04.540
Or some artillery shells.

17:05.599 --> 17:06.640
Yunkui.

17:06.680 --> 17:08.540
The whole line is tight right now.

17:09.000 --> 17:11.119
I have applied to the corps commander in person.

17:11.119 --> 17:13.280
I asked them to transfer troops from other war zones

17:13.280 --> 17:15.480
as reinforcements as soon as possible.

17:15.560 --> 17:16.440
You guys

17:17.200 --> 17:19.040
must hold on.

17:21.640 --> 17:22.520
Go to the front.

17:37.320 --> 17:37.880
Hurry.

17:38.400 --> 17:39.280
This way.

17:41.080 --> 17:41.960
Come here.

17:43.040 --> 17:43.640
Excuse me.

17:47.400 --> 17:48.330
Coming through.

17:48.800 --> 17:49.680
Make way.

17:52.920 --> 17:53.960
Walking wounded here.

17:53.960 --> 17:56.290
Seriously wounded, follow me to the back.

17:56.760 --> 17:57.800
Come here.

17:59.880 --> 18:01.040
There's space here.

18:01.960 --> 18:02.840
Careful.

18:56.280 --> 18:57.940
Brothers of the 87th Brigade,

18:58.840 --> 19:00.040
all stand up!

19:01.520 --> 19:02.440
Salute!

19:03.000 --> 19:04.120
At ease.

19:08.600 --> 19:10.200
Everyone has worked hard

19:10.200 --> 19:11.040
and bled.

19:11.760 --> 19:12.840
Today we repelled the enemy's attack

19:12.840 --> 19:14.080
11 times.

19:14.640 --> 19:16.360
The position changed hands several times,

19:16.360 --> 19:18.090
but we took it back eventually.

19:18.520 --> 19:19.560
Yunkui

19:20.680 --> 19:21.760
thanks you all.

19:22.360 --> 19:23.520
Like I said before,

19:24.080 --> 19:25.200
some of you

19:25.600 --> 19:26.680
are not soldiers,

19:26.880 --> 19:28.120
but because of the emergency,

19:28.120 --> 19:29.320
I couldn't let you go.

19:30.640 --> 19:32.900
The position we are standing on right now

19:33.040 --> 19:34.300
is called Baijiazhai.

19:34.760 --> 19:36.040
The cotton here

19:36.440 --> 19:37.640
is incredibly white,

19:37.800 --> 19:39.660
famous in the surrounding areas.

19:39.960 --> 19:41.280
The cotton farmers here

19:41.280 --> 19:42.720
used to have a good life.

19:43.400 --> 19:45.280
But in just one morning,

19:46.080 --> 19:47.210
the Japanese devils

19:47.960 --> 19:49.240
used their bombs

19:49.760 --> 19:51.620
to level this place to the ground.

19:52.200 --> 19:53.800
Family after family,

19:53.800 --> 19:54.960
their hard-earned,

19:55.160 --> 19:56.600
generational legacy,

19:56.920 --> 19:58.160
harming no one,

19:58.280 --> 19:59.880
was destroyed by the devils.

20:00.640 --> 20:01.300
The devils,

20:01.680 --> 20:02.640
in Northeast China,

20:02.640 --> 20:03.880
in Beiping and Tianjin,

20:03.880 --> 20:06.540
I don't need to say more about their atrocities.

20:06.880 --> 20:08.000
But now,

20:08.280 --> 20:09.940
they want to occupy Shanghai,

20:10.000 --> 20:11.000
occupy Shandong,

20:11.440 --> 20:12.600
occupy Shanxi,

20:12.600 --> 20:14.160
and occupy the whole China.

20:15.040 --> 20:16.080
By then,

20:18.200 --> 20:19.320
how many families

20:20.880 --> 20:22.480
will be destroyed like this?

20:23.160 --> 20:24.240
Today, right here,

20:24.280 --> 20:26.740
more than 500 of our brothers died in battle.

20:27.000 --> 20:28.120
Why did they die?

20:29.040 --> 20:31.370
Because they knew they couldn't retreat.

20:32.120 --> 20:33.650
Why couldn't they retreat?

20:34.160 --> 20:36.240
Because the devils have reached our doorstep.

20:36.240 --> 20:37.570
Wherever we retreat to,

20:37.920 --> 20:40.320
the folks there will be harmed.

20:41.040 --> 20:42.360
So,

20:42.680 --> 20:44.010
we are not afraid to die.

20:44.480 --> 20:45.600
We'll fight them

20:45.920 --> 20:47.000
to the bitter end.

20:47.880 --> 20:48.840
Yunkui.

20:49.440 --> 20:50.760
I beg you all to stay

20:51.280 --> 20:53.240
and fight the Japs with us.

20:55.880 --> 20:56.960
Who wants to stay?

21:04.520 --> 21:05.480
I'll stay.

21:06.960 --> 21:08.420
The Japs won't let us live,

21:08.600 --> 21:09.730
so we'll fight them.

21:09.800 --> 21:10.520
Yes.

21:10.760 --> 21:11.640
Let's fight them.

21:11.640 --> 21:12.900
Yes, let's fight them.

21:12.920 --> 21:13.600
Fight.

21:13.600 --> 21:14.600
Let's fight them.

21:15.040 --> 21:15.800
Good.

21:16.040 --> 21:17.200
Those who want to stay

21:17.200 --> 21:18.520
are all brave men.

21:19.920 --> 21:20.880
I'll stay too.

21:21.960 --> 21:24.520
Before, the Japs broke into my house,

21:24.840 --> 21:25.760
killed my dad,

21:26.280 --> 21:28.320
and crapped in our cooking pot.

21:29.200 --> 21:29.960
They

21:31.080 --> 21:31.800
don't treat

21:31.800 --> 21:33.520
us Chinese as human beings at all.

21:33.520 --> 21:34.640
I want to stay

21:34.640 --> 21:35.640
and kill the Japs.

21:38.760 --> 21:39.680
Officer.

21:41.800 --> 21:42.720
What about

21:43.360 --> 21:44.960
those who don't want to stay?

21:48.240 --> 21:49.640
Those who don't want to stay

21:49.640 --> 21:50.360
can leave.

21:55.480 --> 21:56.320
Xiazi.

21:57.240 --> 21:58.970
If you want to go back, go ahead.

21:59.200 --> 22:00.800
I've long had no home anyway.

22:00.960 --> 22:03.200
My dad was buried alive by the Japs.

22:03.680 --> 22:06.200
My mom was burned alive by the Japs.

22:06.880 --> 22:09.360
My sister was tied to a vat by the Japs

22:09.520 --> 22:10.840
and raped to death.

22:11.360 --> 22:13.080
She wasn't even fourteen.

22:14.240 --> 22:16.640
I've wanted to kill the Japs for a long time.

22:16.920 --> 22:17.760
Officer.

22:18.360 --> 22:19.820
Do those who stay get guns?

22:20.040 --> 22:21.170
We'll give you guns.

22:22.000 --> 22:22.960
I'll stay.

22:23.160 --> 22:25.020
Taking one down makes it worth it.

22:25.480 --> 22:27.140
The Japs burn, kill, and loot.

22:27.640 --> 22:29.040
After raping our people,

22:30.480 --> 22:32.410
they are too stingy to use bullets.

22:32.520 --> 22:33.720
They use two bamboos,

22:34.280 --> 22:35.540
tie their legs to them,

22:35.560 --> 22:36.640
let go,

22:36.960 --> 22:38.880
and tear them apart alive.

22:39.400 --> 22:41.400
Calling them worse than beasts

22:42.040 --> 22:43.800
is an insult to beasts.

22:44.440 --> 22:46.400
I'm going to fight them to the death.

22:46.400 --> 22:47.130
To the death.

22:47.160 --> 22:49.040
Yes, to the death.

22:49.560 --> 22:50.480
To the death.

22:50.480 --> 22:53.400
To the death.

23:06.280 --> 23:06.960
Brothers.

23:12.760 --> 23:13.890
Where are you going?

23:15.720 --> 23:16.920
You cheap bastard.

23:17.360 --> 23:18.600
How dare you leave?

23:20.440 --> 23:21.640
Why can't I leave?

23:21.760 --> 23:23.400
Why can't I leave?

23:23.480 --> 23:24.720
The whole nation is fighting the Japs.

23:24.720 --> 23:26.560
Aren't you part of the nation?

23:26.640 --> 23:28.100
You just said it yourself,

23:28.320 --> 23:29.560
I'm a cheap bastard.

23:29.920 --> 23:31.980
So I'm too cheap for the nation, okay?

23:33.640 --> 23:36.080
If you dare say such things to shake our morale again,

23:36.080 --> 23:37.800
I'll shoot you right now.

23:38.120 --> 23:38.920
Shoot me then.

23:39.320 --> 23:40.160
Shoot me then.

23:40.800 --> 23:42.060
The officer just said,

23:42.120 --> 23:43.920
those who want to leave can leave,

23:43.920 --> 23:45.850
and those who want to stay can stay.

23:49.200 --> 23:49.800
Come here

23:49.840 --> 23:51.040
and look with me.

23:51.160 --> 23:51.920
Stop.

23:53.040 --> 23:54.040
Look who this is.

23:55.280 --> 23:56.040
Look.

23:56.640 --> 23:57.680
Look who this is.

23:58.480 --> 24:00.360
He just died right in front of you.

24:01.080 --> 24:02.160
How did he die?

24:02.880 --> 24:04.140
And what was it all for?

24:14.640 --> 24:16.840
He was killed by a stray bullet.

24:17.800 --> 24:19.480
He wasn't trying to save me.

24:20.040 --> 24:22.360
What does it have to do with me?

24:23.640 --> 24:25.040
I'll kowtow to him, okay?

24:25.360 --> 24:26.420
I'll kowtow to him.

24:27.120 --> 24:28.080
Captain Yu,

24:28.600 --> 24:29.960
you are a great hero.

24:30.040 --> 24:32.080
I kowtow to you.

24:35.000 --> 24:35.840
Captain Yu.

24:35.960 --> 24:37.000
Bullets don't have eyes.

24:37.000 --> 24:38.040
You won't blame me, right?

24:38.040 --> 24:40.700
I'll burn incense for you every year from now on.

24:40.840 --> 24:42.480
I'm just an ordinary citizen.

24:42.480 --> 24:43.640
You are a great hero.

24:44.720 --> 24:46.000
You can't let us

24:46.000 --> 24:48.720
die for you.

24:49.360 --> 24:49.880
Platoon Leader Wang,

24:49.880 --> 24:50.800
I'll kowtow to you too.

24:50.800 --> 24:51.320
I kowtow to you.

24:51.320 --> 24:52.480
Just let me go.

24:52.760 --> 24:53.440
Let me go.

24:53.440 --> 24:54.560
I don't know how to use a gun.

24:54.560 --> 24:55.520
And I can't kill.

24:55.640 --> 24:56.840
Why are you keeping me here?

24:56.840 --> 24:58.680
Keeping me to die?

24:58.680 --> 25:00.610
What the hell are you kneeling for?

25:03.120 --> 25:04.240
Kong Erbao.

25:05.880 --> 25:08.560
Why are your legs so weak?

25:09.600 --> 25:11.880
Are you even a man?

25:13.280 --> 25:14.920
Are you even human?

25:18.240 --> 25:19.160
Get lost!

26:08.400 --> 26:09.400
Stop right there!

26:15.440 --> 26:17.520
Do you dare look at Captain Yu's face?

26:18.240 --> 26:19.520
Make him look at it.

26:23.720 --> 26:24.640
Look!

26:27.720 --> 26:28.680
Do you dare?

26:29.880 --> 26:31.040
Look closely.

26:32.440 --> 26:33.520
You died for us,

26:34.200 --> 26:35.330
but who do we die for?

26:35.680 --> 26:37.440
Is China your country or not?

26:38.120 --> 26:39.200
Is it?

26:40.640 --> 26:41.770
Just because of you,

26:42.440 --> 26:43.080
back in the camp,

26:43.080 --> 26:44.640
I almost shot Captain Yu.

26:45.520 --> 26:46.920
What did he say to me then?

26:47.120 --> 26:48.320
'Tell my mother,

26:49.200 --> 26:50.930
I will die on the battlefield.'

26:51.920 --> 26:52.850
All the soldiers

26:53.320 --> 26:55.400
were pleading here for me to let him go.

26:55.400 --> 26:56.730
What did Captain Yu say?

26:57.080 --> 26:59.080
'I want to die facing the enemy.'

26:59.920 --> 27:01.440
He kept his promise today.

27:02.360 --> 27:03.420
But what about you?

27:03.520 --> 27:05.280
What did you do?

27:06.760 --> 27:07.620
Let me tell you,

27:07.960 --> 27:09.290
anyone can leave today,

27:09.600 --> 27:10.640
but not you.

27:10.920 --> 27:13.040
Have mercy!

27:13.960 --> 27:15.280
I'm just a worm.

27:15.720 --> 27:17.880
I was born a worm.

27:18.080 --> 27:19.280
A worm's life may be worthless,

27:19.280 --> 27:21.000
but it's still a life.

27:21.640 --> 27:23.680
I just live by my own rules.

27:23.720 --> 27:26.280
How am I getting in your way?

27:28.480 --> 27:29.410
I'm telling you,

27:29.880 --> 27:31.360
China is in this state today

27:31.360 --> 27:32.560
because there are too many slugs like you.

27:32.560 --> 27:33.090
Too many.

27:33.120 --> 27:34.480
Completely useless.

27:34.560 --> 27:35.490
Do you know that?

27:35.760 --> 27:36.620
Let me tell you,

27:36.800 --> 27:38.880
today I'm going to teach

27:38.920 --> 27:40.520
a slug like you a good lesson.

27:40.640 --> 27:41.640
Anyone can leave,

27:41.640 --> 27:42.720
but you.

27:43.400 --> 27:44.530
You were just there.

27:44.560 --> 27:46.600
A gentleman's word is his bond.

27:46.600 --> 27:48.260
Who told you I was a gentleman?

27:48.400 --> 27:49.520
Who told you?

27:50.480 --> 27:51.410
I'm telling you.

27:51.560 --> 27:52.840
You're staying here today.

27:52.840 --> 27:54.200
Watch us die.

27:54.280 --> 27:55.280
Watch me die.

27:55.320 --> 27:56.380
But let me tell you,

27:56.680 --> 27:58.440
I'll probably be the last one to die.

27:58.440 --> 27:59.280
From now on,

27:59.280 --> 28:00.280
you are my orderly.

28:00.280 --> 28:01.480
Don't leave my side.

28:08.360 --> 28:09.480
Tell his mother

28:10.000 --> 28:11.440
he was on the battlefield

28:11.600 --> 28:13.880
facing the enemy when he died.

28:17.400 --> 28:18.360
Yes, sir.

28:23.760 --> 28:24.600
Let's go.

28:25.760 --> 28:26.520
Go.

28:26.920 --> 28:27.680
Go.

28:28.080 --> 28:29.520
Go.

28:35.840 --> 28:36.960
Father,

28:37.320 --> 28:38.580
I've put your tea here.

28:39.960 --> 28:41.280
Rest early.

28:43.240 --> 28:44.000
That's all.

28:44.400 --> 28:45.960
You go rest early too.

28:46.240 --> 28:47.640
Sweet dreams.

28:47.640 --> 28:49.440
Sweet dreams.

29:33.200 --> 29:34.120
Normally,

29:34.400 --> 29:36.600
you wouldn't get such an advanced task.

29:36.600 --> 29:38.320
But in these extraordinary times,

29:38.320 --> 29:40.450
we have to make the best of what we have.

29:44.880 --> 29:47.360
This means there's hope for treatment.

29:52.560 --> 29:54.880
This means there is no hope,

29:55.640 --> 29:57.920
but we can't tell the brothers the truth.

30:01.600 --> 30:02.840
Brothers who get this

30:03.480 --> 30:04.610
can only wait to die.

30:04.720 --> 30:06.250
Those with severe injuries

30:06.280 --> 30:08.040
and a weak will to live

30:08.720 --> 30:10.850
will very likely die during the rescue

30:11.200 --> 30:13.360
or even after.

30:13.920 --> 30:17.040
This is a waste of supplies and manpower.

30:18.120 --> 30:19.640
An unsuccessful rescue

30:20.480 --> 30:21.720
will delay other

30:22.160 --> 30:24.040
wounded who might survive.

30:25.280 --> 30:27.340
When I first took over this position,

30:28.280 --> 30:29.740
I wanted to save everyone.

30:30.240 --> 30:32.160
I drew circles as much as possible.

30:32.160 --> 30:33.160
Later,

30:33.440 --> 30:35.770
I was harshly criticized by the director.

30:35.920 --> 30:37.160
He said

30:37.760 --> 30:39.160
I wasn't saving people,

30:40.040 --> 30:42.200
but actually harming them.

30:43.080 --> 30:44.400
It's wartime now.

30:44.680 --> 30:46.080
We are military doctors.

30:46.080 --> 30:47.280
We must stay rational

30:47.440 --> 30:48.760
and know how to make choices

30:48.760 --> 30:50.360
to save more lives.

30:51.400 --> 30:52.880
I understand the reasoning,

30:52.880 --> 30:53.400
but I...

30:53.400 --> 30:55.660
You are the judge of their life and death.

30:57.840 --> 30:58.600
It's cruel,

30:58.600 --> 30:59.730
but this is reality.

31:29.760 --> 31:30.440
Commander.

31:31.000 --> 31:32.320
Luodian is flat with no mountains,

31:32.320 --> 31:33.400
and the surface water is shallow.

31:33.400 --> 31:34.400
We have no way

31:34.440 --> 31:35.770
to dig proper trenches.

31:35.800 --> 31:37.280
We can only build some basic fortifications.

31:37.280 --> 31:38.240
But these fortifications,

31:38.240 --> 31:39.400
under the enemy's heavy artillery,

31:39.400 --> 31:40.120
can't play

31:40.120 --> 31:41.440
any substantial role at all.

31:41.440 --> 31:42.920
We can only defend it with our flesh and blood.

31:42.920 --> 31:44.160
But if we fight the Japanese like this,

31:44.160 --> 31:45.690
we will suffer a great loss.

31:45.720 --> 31:46.760
My suggestion is

31:47.120 --> 31:48.720
to take advantage of the enemy's inability to detect us at night,

31:48.720 --> 31:50.280
use our geographical advantage,

31:50.280 --> 31:51.600
concentrate our firepower to catch them off guard,

31:51.600 --> 31:52.520
and launch a surprise attack on the Japanese.

31:52.520 --> 31:55.280
What we need to do now is hold our position.

31:55.720 --> 31:57.160
Hold the lines one by one

31:57.360 --> 31:58.520
to buy time.

31:58.720 --> 31:59.600
Offense as defense

31:59.600 --> 32:01.080
can also buy us time.

32:01.400 --> 32:02.520
If we defeat the enemy,

32:02.520 --> 32:03.880
we'll buy time when they retreat.

32:03.880 --> 32:05.040
Even if we don't defeat them,

32:05.040 --> 32:06.200
we disrupt their rhythm.

32:06.200 --> 32:07.200
Their attack speed will be hindered,

32:07.200 --> 32:08.760
which also buys us time.

32:08.840 --> 32:12.640
The most important thing on the battlefield is coordinated action.

32:12.640 --> 32:14.320
You are not allowed to move without military orders,

32:14.320 --> 32:16.440
or you will be court-martialed.

32:18.640 --> 32:19.480
Don't worry.

32:20.160 --> 32:21.620
I will consider your plan.

32:22.080 --> 32:22.600
In a few days.

32:22.600 --> 32:23.760
Division Commander.

32:23.760 --> 32:25.160
I am just worried that the opportunity is fleeting.

32:25.160 --> 32:25.890
In a few days,

32:26.080 --> 32:27.000
if the dozen Japanese detachments

32:27.000 --> 32:28.040
are fully deployed,

32:28.040 --> 32:29.700
we will really have no chance.

32:29.880 --> 32:31.080
Execute your orders.

32:35.000 --> 32:36.130
Defending like this

32:36.440 --> 32:38.040
will only increase casualties.

32:38.040 --> 32:39.400
I think the Division Commander's point

32:39.400 --> 32:40.280
is that he's afraid

32:40.280 --> 32:42.010
the casualties will be too high

32:42.320 --> 32:43.320
like the Battle of Hongkou.

32:43.320 --> 32:44.680
I think he's just afraid of taking responsibility.

32:44.680 --> 32:45.240
Report.

32:45.240 --> 32:46.920
How is this different from a suicide mission?

32:46.920 --> 32:48.080
Report, I need to go to the latrine.

32:48.080 --> 32:48.960
Hold it.

32:53.000 --> 32:53.720
Go ahead.

33:05.880 --> 33:06.960
I am Sun Huaiyi.

33:09.480 --> 33:11.480
Generalissimo, this is Sun Huaiyi.

33:11.720 --> 33:13.520
Please give your instructions.

33:14.040 --> 33:14.720
Yes.

33:15.200 --> 33:16.440
Morale is very high.

33:16.760 --> 33:18.640
I promise to complete the mission,

33:18.640 --> 33:20.200
and hold Baijiazhai.

33:35.240 --> 33:37.500
What do you think of Zhang Yunkui's idea?

33:40.880 --> 33:41.800
Division Commander.

33:41.800 --> 33:43.800
I think Zhang Yunkui makes sense.

33:44.160 --> 33:44.920
Look.

33:45.200 --> 33:45.840
Without heavy weapon cover,

33:45.840 --> 33:47.300
we are completely exposed

33:47.480 --> 33:48.840
to the enemy's

33:48.840 --> 33:51.080
aerial bombs and heavy artillery fire.

33:51.360 --> 33:52.480
And the terrain

33:52.640 --> 33:53.280
is not conducive

33:53.280 --> 33:54.940
to building defense in depth.

33:55.200 --> 33:57.200
So each unit is on its own.

33:57.280 --> 33:58.340
If this continues,

33:58.520 --> 34:01.040
our troops will be exhausted sooner or later.

34:01.040 --> 34:02.840
It is only a matter of time before

34:03.840 --> 34:05.480
the Japanese break through our defense line.

34:05.480 --> 34:06.480
Division Commander.

34:06.480 --> 34:08.520
I also think Zhang Yunkui's suggestion is feasible.

34:08.520 --> 34:09.880
If we take the initiative from the flank

34:09.880 --> 34:10.840
and strike them,

34:11.000 --> 34:13.000
it might disrupt their deployment.

34:16.040 --> 34:17.440
In such a large campaign,

34:18.199 --> 34:20.760
all the elites of our army are involved.

34:21.560 --> 34:24.290
Moving an inch will disrupt the whole situation.

34:24.560 --> 34:26.639
Not to mention a mere brigade commander,

34:26.639 --> 34:28.360
even me as a division commander,

34:28.360 --> 34:29.889
the corps commander above,

34:30.120 --> 34:31.760
or the army group commander,

34:32.199 --> 34:33.460
who can call the shots?

34:34.320 --> 34:36.840
The Generalissimo personally oversees everything.

34:36.840 --> 34:37.960
The Theater Commander

34:37.960 --> 34:39.480
has become his messenger.

34:43.679 --> 34:46.810
Now the emphasis is on the integration of the whole army,

34:47.480 --> 34:48.540
following orders.

34:52.560 --> 34:54.679
Private First Class of the 211th Regiment, 36th Division,

34:54.679 --> 34:55.600
Liu Zhenbao.

35:05.240 --> 35:06.040
Which unit?

35:06.160 --> 35:07.840
216th Regiment, 36th Division,

35:07.840 --> 35:09.700
Sergeant Squad Leader Wu Wenjie.

35:11.560 --> 35:13.290
How could the burn be so severe?

35:13.320 --> 35:14.000
Seeing the enemy's shells

35:14.000 --> 35:15.000
were about to hit,

35:15.560 --> 35:17.520
the squad leader tried to get the light machine gun off the position.

35:17.520 --> 35:18.960
But the gun was too hot.

35:19.280 --> 35:20.410
He hugged it and ran.

35:20.520 --> 35:22.780
If it weren't for this light machine gun,

35:22.920 --> 35:24.320
the position would have been lost.

35:24.320 --> 35:26.450
Doctor, can our squad leader be saved?

35:48.880 --> 35:50.560
Give this to the nurse over there.

35:50.560 --> 35:52.160
Thank you, doctor. Let's go.

36:05.560 --> 36:06.480
Let's begin.

36:07.600 --> 36:11.000
Corporal of the 528th Regiment, 88th Division,

36:11.720 --> 36:15.640
Corporal of the 528th Regiment, 88th Division,

36:15.920 --> 36:16.880
Ma Jisheng.

36:18.040 --> 36:19.080
Ma Jisheng.

36:19.720 --> 36:22.960
Corporal of the 583rd Regiment, 98th Division,

36:23.000 --> 36:26.760
Corporal of the 583rd Regiment, 98th Division,

36:31.880 --> 36:33.080
Nameless.

36:35.680 --> 36:39.440
Corporal of the 583rd Regiment, 98th Division,

36:39.600 --> 36:40.640
Nameless.

36:41.280 --> 36:42.760
67th Division,

36:42.840 --> 36:43.800
Yueming.

36:44.520 --> 36:47.250
Gunsmoke filled both banks of the Yangtze River,

36:47.480 --> 36:50.320
and blood dyed the land beneath our feet red.

36:51.200 --> 36:53.560
The disparity in strength between the enemy and us was already great.

36:53.560 --> 36:57.280
But the KMT's command system was corrupt and chaotic,

36:57.560 --> 36:59.200
bypassing the chain of command in battle,

36:59.200 --> 37:01.080
and shifting the blame afterwards.

37:01.080 --> 37:03.920
They equated bravery with consumption.

37:05.000 --> 37:06.640
A large number of sacrifices

37:06.640 --> 37:09.720
could not cleanse this corrupt, deep-rooted illness.

37:10.320 --> 37:13.440
The spiritual mire of old China

37:13.440 --> 37:17.720
was waiting for a completely new cleansing.

37:22.560 --> 37:24.240
Workers, peasants, soldiers, students, and merchants,

37:24.240 --> 37:26.040
let's all come to save the nation.

37:26.040 --> 37:29.600
Pick up our hammers, swords, and guns,

37:29.800 --> 37:33.200
walk out of the factories, fields, and classrooms,

37:33.200 --> 37:34.480
go to the front line,

37:34.480 --> 37:38.760
and step onto the battlefield of national liberation.

37:39.200 --> 37:40.720
Steps matching steps,

37:41.000 --> 37:42.520
arms linking arms,

37:42.880 --> 37:46.400
our team is broad and strong.

37:46.600 --> 37:50.200
The struggle of oppressed brothers all over the world

37:50.200 --> 37:54.080
is moving in one direction.

37:54.320 --> 37:57.920
The voices of millions are shouting for resistance.

37:58.000 --> 37:59.720
The songs of millions

37:59.880 --> 38:03.560
are singing for the revolutionary struggle.

38:03.760 --> 38:07.520
We must build a national defense for the masses.

38:07.520 --> 38:09.480
Everyone, get up and arm yourselves,

38:09.480 --> 38:11.280
down with traitors and lackeys,

38:11.280 --> 38:12.880
and point your guns outward.

38:13.200 --> 38:14.280
We must recover lost land

38:14.280 --> 38:16.720
and down with Japanese imperialism.

38:17.040 --> 38:20.880
Kill all the robbers of the old world.

38:21.480 --> 38:22.720
Good.

38:24.720 --> 38:29.400
The sorghum leaves are so green.

38:30.040 --> 38:35.240
On September 18th, the Japanese soldiers came.

38:35.320 --> 38:39.640
First they occupied the powder magazine,

38:40.720 --> 38:43.040
then they occupied...

38:45.240 --> 38:45.960
Sing.

38:45.960 --> 38:47.000
Keep singing.

38:47.240 --> 38:48.160
Sing the opera.

38:48.280 --> 38:49.400
Gentlemen and lords,

38:49.400 --> 38:50.520
don't rush.

38:50.720 --> 38:52.320
I'll ask her what's going on.

38:53.120 --> 38:54.160
I say, Miss Xiang,

38:54.880 --> 38:57.140
how can you stop singing halfway through

38:57.320 --> 38:58.980
as if you've run out of breath?

38:59.040 --> 38:59.920
Nonsense.

39:00.320 --> 39:02.380
Could I sit here if I ran out of breath?

39:03.040 --> 39:04.900
I just can't muster up the energy.

39:07.520 --> 39:08.920
Miss Xiang said

39:09.000 --> 39:11.480
she can't muster up the energy.

39:11.960 --> 39:12.880
Why can't you muster up the energy?

39:12.880 --> 39:14.120
How can you speak like that?

39:14.120 --> 39:16.520
Are you afraid the officers and soldiers won't tip you?

39:16.520 --> 39:17.400
Impossible.

39:17.640 --> 39:18.160
Quick,

39:18.240 --> 39:19.400
show off a unique skill

39:19.400 --> 39:21.440
to please the lords.

39:22.640 --> 39:23.440
Encore.

39:24.360 --> 39:24.820
Encore.

39:24.960 --> 39:25.840
Good. Encore.

39:33.000 --> 39:37.320
Good, good, good.

39:37.840 --> 39:40.880
Good, good, good.

39:44.600 --> 39:45.040
Why did you fall?

39:45.040 --> 39:45.700
Help him up.

39:45.800 --> 39:46.800
What's going on?

39:48.120 --> 39:48.920
Get up.

39:50.040 --> 39:50.960
Get up.

39:52.000 --> 39:54.480
You are asking for a beating, aren't you?

39:56.920 --> 39:58.000
Stop hitting him.

39:58.440 --> 40:00.600
Stop hitting him.

40:01.640 --> 40:02.920
I'll make you powerless.

40:02.920 --> 40:03.920
Stop hitting him.

40:03.960 --> 40:06.000
I'll kill you.

40:06.880 --> 40:07.480
Don't run.

40:07.520 --> 40:08.360
I was wrong.

40:09.800 --> 40:10.800
Stop hitting him.

40:10.800 --> 40:11.560
Don't run.

40:15.240 --> 40:16.280
What are you doing?

40:16.280 --> 40:17.410
Don't make trouble.

40:18.120 --> 40:19.720
Why are you hitting people?

40:19.920 --> 40:20.840
This is my girl.

40:20.920 --> 40:22.720
I can do whatever I want with her.

40:22.760 --> 40:23.880
We are all poor people.

40:23.880 --> 40:25.120
No one is allowed to bully anyone.

40:25.120 --> 40:25.720
Exactly.

40:25.800 --> 40:26.720
You can't just hit people.

40:26.720 --> 40:27.520
That's right.

40:27.600 --> 40:28.920
Sir, we are acting.

40:29.000 --> 40:29.280
Cut the crap.

40:29.280 --> 40:29.640
Acting.

40:29.640 --> 40:31.600
You can't hit a girl even if you are acting, right?

40:31.600 --> 40:32.600
Come on, hit him.

40:33.320 --> 40:34.240
Hit him.

40:34.800 --> 40:35.760
Hit him. Hit him.

40:36.000 --> 40:37.080
Stop hitting him.

40:37.720 --> 40:38.720
They are acting.

40:38.800 --> 40:39.400
Yes, sir.

40:39.440 --> 40:40.240
Can't you see that?

40:40.240 --> 40:40.920
They are acting.

40:40.920 --> 40:41.850
They are acting.

40:41.920 --> 40:42.560
Fake hitting.

40:42.560 --> 40:44.000
You can't really hit someone even if you are acting.

40:44.000 --> 40:44.730
It's acting.

40:44.920 --> 40:45.640
Fake hitting.

40:45.640 --> 40:46.600
It's fine. We are acting.

40:46.600 --> 40:46.880
Let's go.

40:46.880 --> 40:48.210
I didn't really hit him.

40:48.880 --> 40:49.880
It's fake.

40:50.000 --> 40:51.200
Sit down. Everyone, sit down.

40:51.200 --> 40:51.600
Fake.

40:51.680 --> 40:52.080
Okay.

40:52.200 --> 40:53.130
Let's continue.

40:53.520 --> 40:54.600
You bad old man.

40:55.720 --> 40:56.400
Don't run.

40:56.560 --> 40:57.280
Xiaoyue.

40:58.120 --> 40:59.650
Can you help me comb my hair?

40:59.680 --> 41:00.440
Okay.

41:07.400 --> 41:08.530
Let me see this side.

41:18.120 --> 41:19.520
Han Xiaoyue.

41:33.440 --> 41:35.240
Aren't you going to comb my hair?

41:35.920 --> 41:37.240
Xiaoyue, Xiaoyue.

41:37.680 --> 41:38.280
Xiaoyue.

41:38.880 --> 41:40.040
You are alive.

41:40.160 --> 41:41.320
Alive. Alive.

41:41.440 --> 41:42.920
I am alive.

41:43.040 --> 41:46.400
Do you know I was going crazy looking for you?

41:46.880 --> 41:49.080
I know. I know.

41:53.520 --> 41:54.920
I am alive.

41:59.040 --> 42:00.160
Are you hurt?

42:01.360 --> 42:02.240
I'm fine.

42:03.920 --> 42:05.520
Why are you wearing a uniform?

42:05.520 --> 42:06.400
Kong Erbao.

42:07.160 --> 42:08.640
I was conscripted by them.

42:09.120 --> 42:10.880
Why would they conscript you?

42:11.160 --> 42:12.240
Let's go find the officer.

42:12.240 --> 42:13.760
Can you not be a soldier?

42:14.720 --> 42:15.600
I'm telling you,

42:15.600 --> 42:17.260
these soldiers are all thugs.

42:17.560 --> 42:19.000
The last time I tried to escape,

42:19.000 --> 42:20.200
they almost shot me.

42:20.200 --> 42:21.260
What are you doing?

42:24.880 --> 42:26.080
Platoon Leader Wang.

42:27.120 --> 42:29.440
This... This is my fiancée.

42:30.560 --> 42:31.960
She's from the troop-cheering squad.

42:31.960 --> 42:32.960
We bumped into each other here.

42:32.960 --> 42:33.720
I...

42:34.360 --> 42:36.290
I want to have a quick word with her.

42:37.160 --> 42:38.080
Your fiancée?

42:47.680 --> 42:48.520
Speak.

42:52.160 --> 42:52.880
I...

42:53.680 --> 42:54.940
We'd like to talk here.

43:02.160 --> 43:03.040
Speak now.
